title: Louie CK Unmasked 2008-07-12 CF64k mp3
description:
Unmasked hosted by Ron Bennington with guest Louie C.K. airdate 7-12-08 CF64k mp3

He's starring with Ricky Gervais in a new film entitled "This Side of the Truth". He was the star and creator of HBO's first and only multi-camera sitcom "Lucky Louie". He's had 2 HBO stand-up specials. He had a film premiere at the Sundance Film Festival, and he also wrote and directed "Pootie Tang". He's written for Conan O'Brien, Chris Rock, and he actually appeared on The View once. He is a frequent guest on the nationally syndicated radio show "Opie and Anthony". He's got 2 daughters, an Emmy Award, an ACE Award and (now) his own "Unmasked" interview special on XM.
